profile:
Performance Property Services is a company with over 18 years of experience. We love to help busy homeowners keep their home looking fresh and new! Using our 5-Step Process, we will detail your entire home in just one day. Our services include cleaning exterior windows, cleaning and washing eavestroughs, and cleaning the siding of your home so that your home looks clean, neat, the best on the street!
----
Our team specializes in handwashing exterior home surfaces, including but not limited to windows, eavestroughs, and siding, as pressure washers are harsher and will break and tear those delicate surfaces. We typically use a soft bristle brush and a soft spray washer as opposed to a pressure washer that typically ruins these soft surfaces.
We also powerwash concrete steps, patio decks, stucco siding, and stone surfaces ie. retaining walls. On top of that, our team also can provide services to exterior houses made of stone i.e patio stones, and pool decks. 
----
We provide free home-visitations! Call 1-888-229-1050 for a free quote or text-friendly at 289-668-9924.
Alternatively, we accept quote requests via sales@performancecanada.ca
----
Service is important to us. That is why Performance Property Services strives to complete estimates within 24 hours!
